<br>
The Shark Pool rod in the Qeynos Aqueducts was not there.  Checked 4 times over the course of 36 hours, no rod.  Reported it as a bug - just outta curiosity, created a warrior on another server (Luclin)and ran him down to the pool - the rod is there!  Went down and took note of the exact location (by counting over the cobblestones on the floor from a fixed point).  Went back in with my Wizzie and put my nose right over that point in the pool.  I discovered that every minute and a half or so, the rod would appear for 2 or 3 seconds, then despawn.  Took me several tries, but was able to grab it during that brief window when it appeared.<br>
<br>
Hope this is some help to a questing Wizard who will be as frustrated with this as I was -<br>
<br>
Raytor<br>
Wizard of the 26th season, wielder of the Staff of the Wheel<br>
Prexus<br>
